{"id": "1287947212856365096", "channel_id": "1287947212856365096", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185140987270545408", "author_name": "sin.cos_tan", "author_bot": false, "content": "之前就覺得是不是有問題，總感覺疊命輪怎麼越疊成就次數越少了，但奈何之前沒截過圖不能確定，還以為是自己記錯了。然後昨天特意截了，今天上線一看真的少了<:angry:1239909764163698748> <:cry:1243502872021438475>", "timestamp": "2024-09-24T01:22:24.447000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1287947213405949985", "filename": "IMG_2018.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1204362, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1287947212856365096/1287947213405949985/IMG_2018.png?ex=69cbca90&is=69ca7910&hm=fa22a52f2d57b6acbfa4fec77f60cc3d567e92679295fd308a51c5f344d8031d&"}, {"id": "1287947213821181962", "filename": "IMG_2021.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1160300, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1287947212856365096/1287947213821181962/IMG_2021.png?ex=69cbca90&is=69ca7910&hm=0f42d003b7ea50a37abb7af69b6f95e2d1fc78136de5bc0d16ef44a6f74edd09&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1287947212856365096", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "命輪成就計算錯誤", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1287972844210225174", "channel_id": "1287947212856365096", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176198078026498098", "author_name": "huangyu0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "問就是量子糾纏(O)", "timestamp": "2024-09-24T03:04:15.438000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1287947212856365096", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "命輪成就計算錯誤", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1288042417282351114", "channel_id": "1288042417282351114", "type": 0, "author_id": "793777159637958686", "author_name": "barckcits", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題。\n\n【碎念：主力隊伍技能都升完的時候，就要選下一個要養誰嘛。很遺憾的說，我對角色的愛意程度，並沒有反映在抽卡運上。為了生存和資源，悲憤卻無奈地把愛忍下，先養疊位比較高的，卻發現不能按啟靈排序。啊、我的腦袋已經忙著在相位連敗中找掙扎求存的方法；我的雙眼已經因為卡運不濟悲傷而溢滿淚水，沒有餘力去計算「這個缺一個素材所以按疊位buff順序最有效率要先養的下一個和下下一個是」這種複雜的東西。\n\n拜托貓貓、拜托工工，為無力的大學生填補校園生活的小確憾。喚醒體來了幾次學校（啟靈）已經有紀錄點名了嘛，按出席率（啟靈）電子化排隊服務，提高校園生活體驗，可以有吧。】\n\n附圖：現有排序選項和戈戈的腹肌", "timestamp": "2024-09-24T07:40:42.951000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1288042417534144595", "filename": "EF52AA93-62E4-4808-A369-69201A49425B.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 263613, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288042417282351114/1288042417534144595/EF52AA93-62E4-4808-A369-69201A49425B.jpg?ex=69cc233b&is=69cad1bb&hm=4407e607f2551a511646e2ee6fb300b7e30c8566d1cb7907cfe8a3a5feba5dae&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288042417282351114", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "建議：喚醒體介面增加排序選項「啟靈」", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1288027171448950805", "channel_id": "1288027171448950805", "type": 0, "author_id": "793777159637958686", "author_name": "barckcits", "author_bot": false, "content": "地址：超驗存在漆黑之鏈\n內容：增加觸手時會跳過空格；一回合內增加多於一個觸手時，顯示會少了一個觸手\n推測：道具「潛水罩」（每三回合增加臨時觸手）準備生效前的bug\n理由：跳空格情況常在道具生效的前一回合；非臨時觸手數量達到上限時沒有跳空格\n備註：忘記算實際傷害值有沒有跟觸手顯示一樣少了就過關了，所以不清楚是沒長觸手還是隱形觸手，拍謝\n附圖：1) 沒達到觸手上限、跳2格後長1個觸手、潛水罩道具準備生效；\n2) 沒達到觸手上限、跳1格後長1個觸手、潛水罩道具準備生效；\n3) 沒達到觸手上限、跳1格後長2個觸手、潛水罩道具準備生效；\n4) 沒達到觸手上限、沒有跳格、潛水罩道具生效中；\n5) 達到觸手上限、沒有跳格、潛水罩道具準備生效；\n介面：ipad", "timestamp": "2024-09-24T06:40:08.061000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "😂", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1288027171738095706", "filename": "26EC43BC-9B4B-4E37-B985-A8602C637A6B.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 285309, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288027171448950805/1288027171738095706/26EC43BC-9B4B-4E37-B985-A8602C637A6B.jpg?ex=69cc1508&is=69cac388&hm=951fa4155d5e0964f300101dd24452a3ecb3a6438556b284b14d21916f41ad33&"}, {"id": "1288027172077965344", "filename": "6481D120-D38E-44D1-9D13-05E120B79D64.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 300979, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288027171448950805/1288027172077965344/6481D120-D38E-44D1-9D13-05E120B79D64.jpg?ex=69cc1508&is=69cac388&hm=38e7f214ee689e03b9e9712e7651e294ad17013bf842a5e6e66a07f0d850267f&"}, {"id": "1288027172401057853", "filename": "5FCD16D1-DAF0-4090-87B3-158DD6FCA69E.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 314573, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288027171448950805/1288027172401057853/5FCD16D1-DAF0-4090-87B3-158DD6FCA69E.jpg?ex=69cc1508&is=69cac388&hm=284e7dd1ef9f4d2c24b0975f96e8dc9dbccb79554ac45957a85f315d0f64c23a&"}, {"id": "1288027172723757086", "filename": "C239534D-62C4-40CF-BB37-5039901BAC3A.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 309248, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/128802717